OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK plans radical shake-up  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof aid for climate         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdisasters                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK government is to spend millions 
OL,6, of pounds helping countries prepare for
OL,7, future humanitarian disasters in a     
OL,8, radical shake-up of its development    
OL,9, policy, the BBC has learned.           
OL,11,FA new #150m fund will help poorer      
OL,12,Fcountries get access to money faster in
OL,13,Femergencies and reduce the impact of   
OL,14,Ffuture climate crises.                 
OL,16,FThe change is expected to be part of a 
OL,17,Fnew White Paper designed to make       
OL,18,FBritain's foreign aid spending go      
OL,19,Ffurther while also finding new sources 
OL,20,Fof international finance.              
